g/2000/svg"                         class="img-fluid rounded-4 shadow-lg">                         <rect width="400" height="300" fill="#f5f5f5" />                         <text x="200" y="150" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="24" fill="#C5A028"                             text-anchor="middle" dominant-baseline="middle">üè™ Since 2000 üç∞</text>                     </svg>                 </div>             </div>              <div class="row align-items-center flex-lg-row-reverse mt-5">                 <div class="col-lg-6 mb-4 mb-lg-0 about-text text-start ps-lg-5">                     <h2>Our Mission</h2>                     <p>At Shireen Bakers, we believe that every celebration deserves the perfect centerpiece, and every                         day deserves a touch of sweetness. Our mission is to create exceptional baked goods that bring                         people together and create lasting memories.</p>                     <p>We combine time-honored baking techniques with modern innovation to deliver products that exceed                         expectations. Quality is not just a goal‚Äîit's our promise to every customer who walks through                         our doors.</p>                 </div>                 <div class="col-lg-6 about-image">                     <svg width="100%" height="100%" viewBox="0 0 400 300" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"                         class="img-fluid rounded-4 shadow-lg">                         <rect width="400" height="300" fill="#f5f5f5" />                         <text x="200" y="150" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="24" fill="#C5A028"                             text-anchor="middle" dominant-baseline="middle">üéÇ Quality & Excellence üåü</text>                     </svg>                 </div>             </div>         </section>          <!-- Our Values -->         <section class="about-section">             <h2 class="text-center mb-2" style="font-size: 2.5rem; color: #333;">Our Values</h2>             <p class="text-center mb-5 mx-auto" style="max-width: 700px; color: #666; font-size: 1.1rem;">                 The principles that guide everything we do</p>              <div class="row g-4 row-cols-3 row-cols-md-4 mt-4">                 <div class="col scroll-reveal">                     <div class="value-card h-100">                         <span class="value-icon">üèÜ</span>                         <h3>Quality First</h3>                         <p>We use only the finest ingredients and maintain the highest standards in every product we                             create.</p>                     </div>                 </div>                 <div class="col scroll-reveal">                     <div class="value-card h-100">                         <span class="value-icon">‚ù§Ô∏è</span>                         <h3>Made with Love</h3>                         <p>Every item is crafted with care and passion, ensuring that our love for baking shines                             through.</p>                     </div>                 </div>                 <div class="col scroll-reveal">                     <div class="value-card h-100">                         <span class="value-icon">ü§ù</span>                         <h3>Customer Focused</h3>                         <p>Your satisfaction is our priority. We listen, we care, and we deliver beyond expectations.                         </p>                     </div>                 </div>                 <div class="col scroll-reveal">                     <div class="value-card h-100">                         <span class="value-icon">üå±</span>                         <h3>Fresh Daily</h3>                         <p>We bake fresh every day to ensure you receive the best quality and taste in every bite.</p>                     </div>                 </div>             </div>         </section>          <!-- What We Make -->         <section class="products-showcase px-3">             <h2 class="te